```Object type DEAL_SPLIT is not supported by this endpoint, supported object types [CONTACT, COMPANY, DEAL, TICKET, PRODUCT, QUOTE, LINE_ITEM, FEEDBACK_SUBMISSION, NOTE, MEETING_EVENT, CALL, EMAIL, TASK, COMMUNICATION, ENGAGEMENT, QUOTE_TEMPLATE, TAX, DISCOUNT, FEE, COMMERCE_PAYMENT, POSTAL_MAIL, ORDER, GOAL_TARGET, CART, CAMPAIGN].```
